      <title>议员被捕加深丑闻，岸田遭受新打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/kishida-suffers-fresh-blow-as-lawmaker-s-arrest-deepens-scandal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日，执政党议员首次被捕，首相岸田文雄在日本数十年来最广泛的政治丑闻中再次遭受打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/kishida-suffers-fresh-blow-as-lawmaker-s-arrest-deepens-scandal</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 06:33:57 GMT</pubDate>
